<i>noun</i>: 흥미 [흥ː미], 호기심 [호ː기심], 궁금증 [궁금쯩] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>흥미 [흥ː미]</dt><br>
<dd>interest; curiosity</dd><br>
<dd>마음을 쏠리게 하는 재미.</dd><br>
<dd>Fun, amusement, or entertainment that captivates one's mind.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호기심 [호ː기심]</dt><br>
<dd>curiosity; inquisitiveness</dd><br>
<dd>새롭고 신기한 것을 좋아하거나 모르는 것을 알고 싶어 하는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of liking something new and amazing or a desire to learn something one does not know.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>궁금증 [궁금쯩]</dt><br>
<dd>curiosity</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 궁금한 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being very curious.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>